      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3013 - Jamil narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"There is no harm if a man goes to Mecca, performs Tawaf during the days of Mina, and does not stay overnight there.\""
